sec.p:
Shanmukha et al. [38] introduced three degree and neighborhood degree based novel indices, namely, harmonic-geometric (


      HGI


), neighborhood harmonic-geometric (


      NHGI


) and neighborhood geometric-harmonic (


      NGHI


) indices motivated by the above work. They are defined as follows:

